supergfxctl (5.2.7-4~jammy1) jammy; urgency=medium

  * Fix Launchpad build: remove override_dh_auto_configure — Launchpad
    chroots have no internet access, so curl to sh.rustup.rs fails and
    exits non-zero, killing the build. supergfxctl has no edition=2024
    vendor crates so apt cargo 1.75 builds it directly.
  * Remove curl, ca-certificates from Build-Depends (unused).

 -- Baraka Malila <bmalila87@gmail.com>  Sat, 05 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000

supergfxctl (5.2.7-3~jammy1) jammy; urgency=medium

  * Add python3, curl, ca-certificates to Build-Depends.
  * Install cargo >=1.85 via rustup at configure time for consistency
    with asusctl (guards against future vendor crates using edition="2024").
  * Export CARGO_HOME and prepend ~/.cargo/bin to PATH in debian/rules.

